					<p class="lead mb-4 about-text">
						Finnish Trainer is a comphrehensible learning application aimed to help
						memorising vocabulary while reading texts.
						Not only there are many text inside this application you can also use
						external ones to check you vocab.
						When reading a text you can click each token and get translation with
						grammatical information about each word.
						If it seems unknown to you, you can save it and look it up later to
						memorise it.
						Additionally for the better learning process you can play a little game with
						those.
						If you would like to get an account you have to ask an admin to add
						you.
						Then you will be able to access it any time and make the process of
						learning more pleasant!
						So go to FINISH and learn FINNISH!
